  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Medical data that contain facial images are particularly sensitive as they retain important&#xD;
      personal biometric identity, privacy protection. We developed a novel technology called&#xD;
      &quot;Digital Mask&quot; (DM), based on real-time three-dimensional (3D) reconstruction and deep&#xD;
      learning algorithm, to extract disease-relevant features but remove patient identifiable&#xD;
      features from facial images of patients.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
