  <primary_outcome>
    <measure>Diagnostic consistency</measure>
    <time_frame>baseline</time_frame>
    <description>For each eye, both the diagnosis from the original videos and the diagnosis from the DM-reconstructed videos were recorded and compared. If the two diagnoses were consistent, it suggests that the reconstruction would be precise enough in clinical practice.</description>
